10:T45e,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Movie","name":"Yu Pui Tsuen II","description":"Before Michael Mak’s Sex And Zen became a cult favourite in the ’90s, there was Ho Fan’s Yu Pui Tsuen (The Carnal Prayer Mat, 1987). But without sex bomb Amy Yip, coarse humour or lesbian love affairs, Yu Pui Tsuen had to rely on the nudity and sex from his cast of relative unknowns to save the day.  When a young man dreams that he drowns after a night of carnal passion, he asks a buddhist monk to translate the experience for him. The monk replies that the dream is a warning not to indulge the pleasures of the flesh to excess, but the man ignores his advice, marrying a virgin and making love to her constantly. However, after several torrid affairs, the man begins to realise the sagacity of the monk's warning.","image":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3NwBn6zPY6yXCqfxEHmEgGh8Jgc.jpg","datePublished":"1987-10-15","numberOfEpisodes":null,"countryOfOrigin":"HK","inLanguage":"cn","genre":["Drama","Fantasy","Romance"],"aggregateRating":{"@type":"AggregateRating","ratingValue":5.2,"bestRating":10,"ratingCount":27}}5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$10"}}],["$","$L11",null,{"initialDrama":{"id":"70f57f2c-ef6b-408c-9b58-63267fc16c46","tmdb_id":410119,"imdb_id":"tt0345219","content_type":"movie","title":"Yu Pui Tsuen II","original_title":"足本玉蒲團","overview":"Before Michael Mak’s Sex And Zen became a cult favourite in the ’90s, there was Ho Fan’s Yu Pui Tsuen (The Carnal Prayer Mat, 1987). But without sex bomb Amy Yip, coarse humour or lesbian love affairs, Yu Pui Tsuen had to rely on the nudity and sex from his cast of relative unknowns to save the day.  When a young man dreams that he drowns after a night of carnal passion, he asks a buddhist monk to translate the experience for him. The monk replies that the dream is a warning not to indulge the pleasures of the flesh to excess, but the man ignores his advice, marrying a virgin and making love to her constantly. However, after several torrid affairs, the man begins to realise the sagacity of the monk's warning.","poster_path":"/3NwBn6zPY6yXCqfxEHmEgGh8Jgc.jpg","backdrop_path":"/lhHxiwtHq1GG5MhPyWaETvKjoGg.jpg","release_date":"1987-10-15","first_air_date":null,"status":"published","original_language":"cn","origin_country":["HK"],"genres":[{"id":18,"name":"Drama"},{"id":14,"name":"Fantasy"},{"id":10749,"name":"Romance"}],"popularity":9.4732,"vote_average":5.2,"vote_count":27,"runtime":90,"number_of_seasons":null,"number_of_episodes":null,"created_at":"2026-01-26T16:52:13.103266+00:00","updated_at":"2026-02-22T21:01:46.312+00:00","tagline":null,"homepage":null,"budget":0,"revenue":0,"production_companies":[],"production_countries":[{"name":"Hong Kong","iso_3166_1":"HK"}],"spoken_languages":[],"networks":[],"last_air_date":null,"in_production":null,"tmdb_status":"Released","content_rating":null,"keywords":[],"alternative_titles":[{"type":"","title":"The Carnal Prayer Mat","iso_3166_1":"HK"},{"type":"","title":"Sex and Zen: The Virgin Years","iso_3166_1":"GB"},{"type":"","title":"浮世风情绘","iso_3166_1":"HK"},{"type":"original title","title":"Fu shi feng qing hui","iso_3166_1":"HK"},{"type":"","title":"Yu Pui Tsuen II","iso_3166_1":"HK"},{"type":"Cantonese title","title":"Fau sai fung ching kooi","iso_3166_1":"HK"},{"type":"","title":"正宗肉蒲團","iso_3166_1":"HK"},{"type":"","title":"足本玉蒲团","iso_3166_1":"CN"},{"type":"","title":"正宗玉蒲团","iso_3166_1":"CN"},{"type":"","title":"The Carnal Sutra Mat","iso_3166_1":"US"},{"type":"","title":"육보단","iso_3166_1":"KR"},{"type":"","title":"Yu Pui Tsuen","iso_3166_1":"US"},{"type":"","title":"浮世风情绘","iso_3166_1":"CN"}],"videos":[],"watch_providers":{"results":{}},"wikidata_id":null,"tvdb_id":null,"wikipedia_url":null,"overview_source":"tmdb","import_batch_id":null,"import_batch_name":null,"imported_at":"2026-02-07T14:49:53.785279+00:00","region":"CN","main_poster":"/3NwBn6zPY6yXCqfxEHmEgGh8Jgc.jpg","images":{"logos":[],"posters":[{"width":2000,"height":3000,"file_path":"/3NwBn6zPY6yXCqfxEHmEgGh8Jgc.jpg","iso_639_1":"zh","vote_average":3.334},{"width":500,"height":750,"file_path":"/mrV7CcjEtuXtXjykopDUiIgIQru.jpg","iso_639_1":"zh","vote_average":1.75},{"width":500,"height":750,"file_path":"/u7CGXhUV9MUxjJdjLy4mHbDVUfX.jpg","iso_639_1":"zh","vote_average":1.75},{"width":2000,"height":3000,"file_path":"/dnMPB8rLZQ9HGuOWD6teyXHjJOQ.jpg","iso_639_1":"zh","vote_average":0}],"backdrops":[{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/lhHxiwtHq1GG5MhPyWaETvKjoGg.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/1L6QIvnkZRBY4Ks8Bn1qfNBpLCX.jpg","iso_639_1":"zh","vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/oYgUMTpQc1BNtPBUZRbdGGOUB63.jpg","iso_639_1":"zh","vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T06:47:20.533+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Yu Pui Tsuen II","runtime":90,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Before Michael Mak’s Sex And Zen became a cult favourite in the ’90s, there was Ho Fan’s Yu Pui Tsuen (The Carnal Prayer Mat, 1987). But without sex bomb Amy Yip, coarse humour or lesbian love affairs, Yu Pui Tsuen had to rely on the nudity and sex from his cast of relative unknowns to save the day.  When a young man dreams that he drowns after a night of carnal passion, he asks a buddhist monk to translate the experience for him. The monk replies that the dream is a warning not to indulge the pleasures of the flesh to excess, but the man ignores his advice, marrying a virgin and making love to her constantly. However, after several torrid affairs, the man begins to realise the sagacity of the monk's warning."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"足本玉蒲团","runtime":91,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"故事描述四百年前一个风流才子，命犯桃花，一夕得一荒唐绮梦，初则徵歌逐色，继而沉沦欲海，终至惨遭灭顶 ，于是一惊而醒，上山问道于高僧，但与高僧激辩后， 才子仍深信“人生朝露，及时行乐”的哲学，于是展开 其纵横欲海之“性路历程”。  才子首先娶得美人归，旦旦而伐，夜夜笙歌，知丈人看不过眼，乃以上京赴考为名，却是到处猎艳为实，于是抛弃妻，云游四海。首先在一庸堂钓得一上香美女，几番波折，终诣鱼水之欢。艳妇之夫盛怒之下以牙还牙，将该才子之妻多番淫辱报复，继而将之卖落青楼，为万人荐枕。  及后才子在青楼召妓，巧遇其妻，其妻无颜相见，自缢而死。才子抚尸痛哭，悔之已晚，方知万恶淫为首，轮回报应，半点无差，至此大澈大悟，遁入空门，了此残生。  本片只是平铺直叙了一个“淫人妻女者被人淫”的故事，且在色情之余，着力刻画了未央生与玉香这两个角色。未央生淫了别人的妻子，但是却害怕自己也落入别人的下场，这一点，从片头那段魔幻主义的歌舞就可以看得出来。  本片1996年改名《足本玉蒲团》重映"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"육보단","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"청년시절 여인을 탐하는 꿈을 자주 꾸던 이운생은 소향과 결혼한 후, 과거보러 떠난 길에 명주실 짜는 옥분을 알게 되어 사랑에 빠진다. 옥분의 남편 관녹지는 위자료를 받아낸 뒤, 운생의 집에 머슴으로 들어가 소향과 밀애후 도피행각을 하기에 이른다. 복수가 목적이었던 곽녹지는 소향을 홍루에 팔아버린 후, 절에 들어간다. 한편, 집에 돌아와 장인으로부터 아내가 상사병에 걸려 죽었다는 말을 듣고 다시 길을 떠나다 홍루에서 기생이 된 아내를 만나게 된 운생은 모든 사실을 알게된다. 소향이 고심 씉에 목을 매어 자살하자, 이운생은 삭발 후 절에 들어가 판녹지와 함께 큰스님을 모신다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"足本玉蒲團","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"《浮世風情繪》（英語：The Carnal Sutra Mat）。1996年改名《足本玉蒲團》重映。\r 風流才子不顧高僧所言，深信「人生朝露，及時行樂」，雖然娶得美人歸卻還是夜夜笙歌，得知丈人看不過眼，便以上京赴考為名出外獵艷。後來釣得一艷婦，而艷婦之夫盛怒之下將該才子之妻多番淫辱，並將之賣落青樓。後來才子召妓，而其妻因無顏相見，自縊而死，才子才後悔莫及、撫屍痛哭，卻也為時已晚。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Cielesna sutra","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Młodemu mężczyźnie przyśniło się, że utonął po nocy pełnej  namiętnych uniesień, prosi więc buddyjskiego mnicha, aby objaśnił mu ukryte znaczenie snu. Mnich odpowiada, że było to ostrzeżenie, by nie popadać w nadmierne przyjemności cielesne.  Mężczyzna ignoruje jednak jego radę. Poślubia dziewicę i spędza z nią cały czas wolny na uprawianiu seksu. Jednak po pewnym czasie mężczyzna zaczyna zdawać sobie sprawę że ostrzeżenia mnicha zaczynają się sprawdzać ."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Bahasa melayu","iso_639_1":"ms","iso_3166_1":"MY","english_name":"Malay"},{"data":{"title":"足本玉蒲團","runtime":90,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"《浮世風情繪》（英語：The Carnal Sutra Mat）。1996 年改名《足本玉蒲團》重映。\r 風流才子不顧高僧所言，深信「人生朝露，及時行樂」，雖然娶得美人歸卻還是夜夜笙歌，得知丈人看不過眼，便以上京赴考為名出外獵艷。後來釣得一艷婦，而艷婦之夫盛怒之下將該才子之妻多番淫辱，並將之賣落青樓。後來才子召妓，而其妻因無顏相見，自縊而死，才子才後悔莫及、撫屍痛哭，卻也為時已晚。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"Nhục Bồ Đoàn 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Trước khi Sex And Zen của Michael Mak trở thành bộ phim được yêu thích trong thập niên 90, đã có Yu Pui Tsuen của Ho Fan (The Carnal Pray Mat, 1987). Nhưng không có bom sex Amy Yip, sự hài hước thô tục hay những mối tình đồng tính nữ, Yu Pui Tsuen phải dựa vào cảnh khỏa thân và tình dục từ dàn diễn viên họ hàng vô danh của mình để cứu vãn tình thế. Khi một chàng trai mơ thấy mình chết đuối sau một đêm đam mê xác thịt, anh ta đã nhờ một nhà sư Phật giáo dịch lại trải nghiệm đó cho anh ta. Nhà sư trả lời rằng giấc mơ là lời cảnh báo không nên quá ham mê thú vui xác thịt, nhưng người đàn ông đã phớt lờ lời khuyên của ông, cưới một trinh nữ và làm tình với cô ấy liên tục. Tuy nhiên, sau nhiều chuyện nóng nảy, người đàn ông bắt đầu nhận ra sự khôn ngoan trong lời cảnh báo của nhà sư."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Voordat Sex And Zen van Michael Mak in de jaren negentig een cultfavoriet werd, was er Yu Pui Tsuen van Ho Fan (The Carnal Prayer Mat, 1987). Maar zonder seksbom Amy Yip, grove humor of lesbische liefdesaffaires moest Yu Pui Tsuen vertrouwen op de naaktheid en seks van zijn cast van relatieve onbekenden om de boel te redden. Wanneer een jonge man droomt dat hij verdrinkt na een nacht vol vleselijke hartstocht, vraagt ​​hij een boeddhistische monnik om de ervaring voor hem te vertalen. De monnik antwoordt dat de droom een ​​waarschuwing is om niet overmatig te genieten van de geneugten van het vlees, maar de man negeert zijn advies, trouwt met een maagd en bedrijft voortdurend de liefde met haar. Na een aantal verzengende zaken begint de man echter de scherpzinnigheid van de waarschuwing van de monnik te beseffen."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":191561,"adult":false,"title":"Yu Pui Tsuen III","video":false,"overview":"Ming Dynasty secret agent Ling Ling Ling (000) is assigned to investigate a drug poisoning involving a performance enhancing drug in the brothel, Ying Chun Kwok. Ling thought hard and finally came up a disguise as the author of Yuk Po Tuen (Sex and Zen) to sneak into the brothel. The prostitutes in order to get their names into the book all tempted Ling, who in order to appaise the ladies, turned the book into a book of dirty stories. One day, a blind servant Yuk Chu Nui (Jade Virgin) is auditioned, Ling learned that the buyer would receive the drug, so he bidded up the prices hoping to receive the evidence. Who would expect that someone else is bidding with a higher price?","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.4996,"vote_count":30,"poster_path":"/d4mMa9JWyBLp1MK5eDDDujU5C9A.jpg","release_date":"1996-08-10","vote_average":5.4,"backdrop_path":"/n2b9fTgkRosM0UrAdD7UkkHz5Ky.jpg","original_title":"大內密探之零零性性","original_language":"zh"},{"id":921436,"adult":false,"title":"Escape","video":false,"overview":"After completing his required decade of military service and being honored as a hero, a North Korean sergeant makes a sudden shocking attempt to defect to the South, risking life and limb for the chance to finally determine his own destiny.","genre_ids":[28,18,53],"medi